The paper focuses on the analysis and prediction of social communities in social media, which falls under the scope of social network analysis. Therefore, cs.SOC is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves the extraction and selection of network features, which can be categorized under cs.SI and cs.LG. The use of classification models for prediction can be classified under cs.SD and cs.IR, as it involves machine learning and information retrieval techniques.
